DS3: A System-Level Domain-Specific System-on-ChipSimulationFramework
Namespace List
Here is a list of all namespaces with brief descriptions:
 NclustersThis file contains the information about the clusters in the SoC
 NcommonThis file contains all the common parameters used in DASH_Sim
 NCP_modelsThis file contains the code for dynamic scheduling with Constraint Programming
 NDASH_Sim_coreThis file contains the simulation core that handles the simulation events
 NDASH_Sim_utilsThis file contains functions that are used by DASH_Sim
 NDASH_Sim_v0This file is the main() function which should be run to get the simulation results
 NDASH_SoC_parserThis file contains the code to parse DASH-SoC given in config_file.ini file
 NDTPMThis file contains the code for the DTPM module
 NDTPM_policiesThis file contains the DVFS policies
 NDTPM_power_modelsThis file contains functions that are used by the DVFS mechanism and PEs to get performance, power, and thermal values
 Njob_generatorThis file contains the code for the job generator
 Njob_parserThis file contains the code to parse jobs given in config_file.ini file
 Nprocessing_elementThis file contains the process elements and their attributes
 Nrun_Scheduling_Case_Study
 Nrun_Scheduling_Case_Study_example
 NschedulerThis file contains all schedulers in DASH-Sim
